General.Name: Renegade Exploration Ltd
General.Description: Renegade Exploration Limited discovers, acquires, explores for, and develops mineral deposits in Australia. It primarily explores for copper and gold deposits. The company holds a 23% interest in the Carpentaria Joint Venture project located in the Cloncurry region of Queensland. It also holds an option to acquire a 75% interest in the North Isa project located in Queensland. The company was formerly known as Overland Resource Limited. Renegade Exploration Limited was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
